0 ls0 ws0">tory. </div><div class="t m55c xb1 h2b y470 ff5 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The authors share thought-</div><div class="t m55d x30 h2b y471 ff5 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">provoking images of the closing </div><div class="t m55e x30 h2b y3a0 ff5 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">scenes of Jesus&apos; life and the </div><div class="t m55f x30 h2b y472 ff5 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">impact of His final words. People </div><div class="t m560 x30 h2b y21f ff5 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of all walks of life stood there and </div><div class="t m561 xc1 h2b ydf ff5 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">listened. Some observers almost </div><div class="t m562 xc1 h2b y1c8 ff5 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">believed, some had believed, and </div><div class="t m563 xc1 h2b y9f ff5 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">some truly believed—at least </div><div class="t m564 xc1 h2b y16a ff5 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">when it was over. </div><div class="t m565 x99 h2b y473 ff5 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Which point of view would be </div><div class="t m566 xc1 h2b y10a ff5 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">yours? Where would you stand? </div><div class="t m567 x99 h2b y145 ff5 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Those looking for hope and </div><div class="t m568 xc1 h2b y474 ff5 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">courage will find them in the </div><div class="t m569 xc1 h2b y29c ff5 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">words and actions of Jesus that </div><div class="t m56a xad h2b y272 ff5 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">day. Stand at the Cross —and be </div><div class="t m56b xad h2b y475 ff5 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">changed. </div><div class="t m56c xad h2b y7c ff5 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Paper, 128 pages. </div><div class="t m56d xad h2b y476 ff5 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">US $8.99, Cdn $12.99. </div><div class="t m56e x8f h10 y196 ff5 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Prices subject to change </div><div class="t m56f xa7 h3a y477 ff1 fs12 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Available at your </div><div class="t m570 xa5 h3a y1d8 ff1 fs12 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">local ABC. Call </div><div class="t m571 x81 h3a y478 ff1 fs12 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1-800-765-6955.